Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.72,0:00:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大清早的就練拳麼  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千雨同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.69,0:00:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp163}　{\fsp0}Magia Erebea{\r}\N據說是依文潔琳從前寫下的黑暗魔法的卷軸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.10,0:00:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…並不是普通的咒文卷軸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.45,0:00:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「如果你要走光明大道就不要打開」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「如果選擇黑暗的話就打開看看」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.27,0:00:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:49.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你早就已經決定好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.46,0:00:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣  我也在好好看著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.90,0:01:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點事我看得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.21,0:02:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「父親的道路  還是師父的道路！？」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何  決定好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:54.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  光明和黑暗  你選哪邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.39,0:02:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  你果然還是想走你父親的路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  這也不無道理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千雨同學  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個選擇或許真的很亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會還在猶豫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是對是錯  不做做看怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這是個重大決定  我能理解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那是你自己選擇的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己走出的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管它亂來不亂來的  拿出自信來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好見證的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我的心意已決
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深思熟慮後的結論  或許是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許會被黑暗吞沒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:08.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了今後也能和大家一起前進
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了追上父親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我願放手一搏…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉坎先生  我選擇黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真出人意料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過小子  你不用追你父親了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是父親  怎麼模仿也不能成為他的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然我有黑暗的潛力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只有窮究這一潛力  才能追上父親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也…很喜歡師父
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛的告白啊  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是這個意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你太小看黑暗了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那卷軸  一旦打開了它  可是會很艱苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這卷軸非同尋常這點我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經做好覺悟了  一定會突破難關的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.23,0:05:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你說的哦  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就讓你好好體會到黑暗可不容你小覷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師父
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克服這一難關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:03.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果挺不過去你就只有一死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼回事  為什麼她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了  會很艱苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  要塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑快跑  不然要被活埋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到最後會碰到這麼老套的陷阱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  你還行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  是出口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:37.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險吶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到遺跡會整個崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為會死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷吧  和香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來  你真的變堅強了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在遺跡裡發現的你說要加入我們的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還真不知道該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:11.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  和香發現陷阱的能力一級棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能派用場
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:17.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個年紀就有這等能力  你究竟是在哪學到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:23.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  是在課外活動上…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  期待已久的分贓時間到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不枉我們辛苦  收穫頗豐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  你真的不要財寶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不用了  我要這個就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:47.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要賣的話  應該也很值錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是和香在找的魔法道具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  多虧了各位  終於得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp220}　{\fsp0}Comptina  Daemonia{\r}\N能看穿對方名字的魔法道具「鬼神童謠」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍有點壞壞的感覺～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,0:08:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有二十米長的大塊頭卻有如此高的機動能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外加充沛的體力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  龍真是個強大的種族  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓忍法  縛鎖爆炎陣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不動明王真言  不動一字咒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:00.96,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（梵文）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.60,0:09:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:11.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓不會被黑龍打敗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊退黑龍的任務完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:33.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下手有些太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫它治療
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不勝感激
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  注意不要把一邊的角也治好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.97,0:09:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Adeat
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東風檜扇  南風末廣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.45,0:09:56.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  能治癒那麼大的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙  傷治好了還要再幹一場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木乃香  快退下…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能再做壞事啦  明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.02,0:10:22.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣  按照委託  把它的一支角折斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.75,0:10:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在明年重新長出角來之前  它應該不會回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Adeat
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來  木乃香你真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢  你稱讚我也沒好處的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要這麼說的話  楓才是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴著眼罩能贏過龍  這是有多強？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  這是修行的一環…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這點本事還完全不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  楓你不也受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你治好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來木乃香的治癒術越來越嫻熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開門  開門
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那不是黑龍的角嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位幹得太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.11,0:11:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞇瞇眼的大姐  傳言你就是真正的忍者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相比之下  住在我們店裡的這兩個窩囊廢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我們吧  老闆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.70,0:11:37.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是黑龍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  襲擊村子的兩條龍中  只擊退了其中一條
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  聽說有其他旅行中的賞金獵人擊退了另外一條
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:54.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:12:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚些要來我們店裡啊  請你們吃一頓邊境最好吃的飯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.52,0:12:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  真是不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.31,0:12:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在原本的世界中我的能力毫無用場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到在這裡竟然能讓人們這麼高興
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  木乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木乃香？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很少見到木乃香那麼沮喪的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我並沒有…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  涅吉小弟也會平安無事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那和明日菜一定也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神來啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  大小姐確實在這一帶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.41,0:12:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們卻為了打敗龍而浪費了時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說這支角能賣大價錢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小木…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小剎～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:56.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:12:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜別來無恙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:01.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小剎  小剎  我好想你啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大  大大大  大小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜你也沒事真太好了～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦  木乃香你冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  這下涅吉魔社四人匯合了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不明白怎麼回事  總之祝賀你們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:17.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜又變強了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看得出嗎  楓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做賞金獵人時不僅打倒魔獸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還反擊了襲擊我們的賞金獵人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.03,0:13:39.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  接下來就差和涅吉還有大家匯合了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  燒退不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和之前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:13:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那女人到底做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:01.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有她去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人？  是說長得像依文一樣的傢伙麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:10.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是依文的劣化複製品  人造靈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在估計在小子體內呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓他能運用黑暗力量而給他試煉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子如果不能經受住這場試煉  就再也不會醒來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少他的身體將不能再使用魔法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒聽說這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你既然知道  就應該阻止…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不正常的方法  這點風險應該早就做好覺悟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不準備的話可是會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:14:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師父
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是精神上的死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}　Ensis Exsequens{\r}\N哦  斷罪之劍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是在模仿我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  你不也從一開始就有戰鬥的打算麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到竟然有愚蠢到自己選擇黑暗的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:30.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地點變了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我要冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.15,0:15:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡大概是我的腦內
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.54,0:15:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個師父應該也不是本人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗是什麼  小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與光相反的影
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與白晝相反的黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生與死  善與惡  秩序與混沌  合理與不合理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:52.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在這裡你所需要的是更單純的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,lic lac la lac lilac
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:57.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}veniant spiritus glaciales{\r}\N來吧  冰之精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}extendantur aeri{\r}\N充滿於大氣之中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}tundram et glaciem loci noctis albae{\r}\N帶來白夜之國的凍土與冰河吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Crystallizatio Tellustris　{\r}\N凍結的大地！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:14.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那既是吞噬一切的黑洞  也是原初的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是次元的混沌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,lic lac la lac lilac
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  冰精！來吧  風精！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.13,0:16:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Nivis Casus　{\r}\N冰爆！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.03,0:16:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能理解其中道理  你就會在這裡被我殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.50,0:16:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞噬一切的原初的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要冷靜  這個師父不過是由我的記憶和想像造出的幻覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是我的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.01,0:16:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依我的印象  我對師父的印象…對師父的印象…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:53.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,印…象…完全贏不了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  你其實早已理解其中意義
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆裂寸勁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了  我忘了要留地方立足了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.94,0:17:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬動！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鈞一髮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  是不是做得過火了點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  今天也向前邁進了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不能停止修行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:06.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是啥東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古菲同學  我找你找得可辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是不顯眼的幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好過分  古菲同學你好壞好壞好壞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.78,0:18:27.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家那麼努力找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的  開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.51,0:18:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好嗎  小夜崽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊  早已死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧你能在那麼大的世界裡找到我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是自己一個人  是怎麼做到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.61,0:18:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實發生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  小弟  已經不行了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是幾百個小時罷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:18:59.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個師父是我的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:09.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰勝她也就意味著戰勝我自己的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  要怎麼打敗她！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.99,0:19:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Sagitta Magica Series Fulguralis{\r}\N魔法之射手  雷之九矢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷華崩拳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓我驚訝  你竟然還能有如此的行動力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp340}　{\fsp0}Phantasmagoria{\r}\N在這無法入眠  無法逃避  甚至不允許死亡的幻想空間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能堅持這麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.28,0:20:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意志力堪稱奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你的精神力也會迎來極限的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是第幾次了  七十次左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:11.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回你還能站得起來嗎  小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.62,0:20:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.58,0:20:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  大叔  藥草不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再給我點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  小姐  你也夠厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.65,0:20:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然兩天兩夜不睡  照顧著小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.81,0:20:32.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙要是出了什麼事  有一半是我的責任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:39.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  這到底要持續多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼久了  很不妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實  不說肉體上的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神上說不定真的已經到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Phantasmagoria{\fsp65}　{\r}\N現在小子所在的幻想空間的感覺時間是現實的幾倍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算下來他至少持續戰鬥了十天以上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常人已經無法保持自我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子已經很了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十天？那…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp135}　{\fsp0}Phantasmagoria{\r}\N沒錯  如果小子再找不出突破幻想空間的方法的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就出局了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我之前所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.41,0:21:22.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要麼再也醒不過來  要麼再也不能用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天破曉時大概就是極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:28.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐你也做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.44,0:21:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  不行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來  通向光明和黑暗的兩條路都斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  這樣也好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.93,0:21:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你的同伴救活你  回到家裡  忘了你父親的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.94,0:21:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那個學園裡和大家一起快樂地活下去也不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:22:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做得很好了  小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.67,0:22:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Nivis Casus　{\r}\N冰爆！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.82,0:22:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  終於勢均力敵了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看著  好好品嚐  好好記住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.91,0:22:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的力量源泉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.39,0:22:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本能的衝動  你最大的動力  你的心像風景
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.50,0:22:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.36,0:22:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你還贏不了  真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.03,0:22:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打敗了  這樣還不夠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.00,0:22:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也理所當然  我怎麼可能打敗師父…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.94,0:22:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這笨蛋涅吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.39,0:22:57.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  誇下那麼大的海口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.78,0:22:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就這麼放棄了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.81,0:23:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,lic lac la lac lilac
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}veniant spiritus glaciales obscurantes　{\r}\N來吧  冰精！暗之精靈！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.57,0:23:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}cum obscurationi flet tempestas nivalis　{\r}\N聽令於黑暗吹起永夜的冰雪吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.17,0:23:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  明日菜同學  我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.10,0:23:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  你其實早已理解其中意義
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.57,0:23:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  對啊  我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.87,0:23:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了  小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.52,0:23:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Nivis Tempestas Obscurans　{\r}\N暗夜吹雪！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.91,0:23:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就在大家對我說的話語之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.05,0:23:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有再大的煩惱也別去在意  把它藏在心底前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.00,0:23:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是怨恨別人  逃避事實而得到的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.93,0:23:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是你足以引以為傲的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.30,0:23:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使摔得一身是泥  仍然要向前邁進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.01,0:23:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.44,0:23:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Magia Erebea{\fsp77}　{\r}\N黑暗魔法  那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.26,0:24:03.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論善還是惡  堅強還是弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.89,0:24:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都原封不動地接受並吞噬掉的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.89,0:24:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Complexio　{\r}\N掌握！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.84,0:24:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.55,0:24:20.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.37,0:24:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp23}　{\fsp0}Magia Erebea{\r}\N終於學會黑暗魔法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.60,0:24:27.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是由我的記憶構成的我的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.53,0:24:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是我的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.45,0:24:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒你並不代表就通過這個試煉了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.71,0:24:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你花太多時間了  不過我也不追究了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.87,0:24:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.48,0:24:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的成果吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.21,0:25:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.35,0:25:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒好嗎  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.10,0:25:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經等不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.19,0:25:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天開始亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.44,0:25:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要用那把匕首取消試煉的話  必須在日出之前
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.21,0:25:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.82,0:25:33.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…果然還是不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.97,0:25:42.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  老師  我沒能相信你到最後一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.11,0:25:47.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只要你沒事的話  還有很多方法可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.60,0:25:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  千雨同學
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.95,0:25:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.89,0:26:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.31,0:26:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千雨同學  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.87,0:26:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要醒就給我早點醒啊  你這臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.50,0:26:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然像故事裡一樣  在最後的最後才醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.44,0:26:18.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.40,0:26:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  很危險的…千雨同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.38,0:26:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知不知道浪費了我多少感情啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.41,0:26:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  等等…我不知道為什麼渾身都痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.97,0:26:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.08,0:26:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.51,0:26:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你醒啦  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.04,0:26:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉坎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.87,0:26:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔  你這什麼反應
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.78,0:26:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是不得已陪了他整整兩天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.94,0:26:47.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等  很危險的啊  千雨小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.64,0:26:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰  看到他平安都該掉兩滴眼淚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.40,0:26:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.81,0:26:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  小子  要好好感謝她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.38,0:27:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她照顧了瀕死的你整整兩天兩夜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.76,0:27:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  千雨同學她…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.15,0:27:05.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千雨同學  謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.34,0:27:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴  別以為一句道謝就能還清這筆債！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.24,0:27:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我跪下  成為我的奴隸！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.57,0:27:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣  你做得很好  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.69,0:27:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣總算站上起跑線了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.01,0:27:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把魔力集中到雙臂上看看
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.56,0:27:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙臂…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.65,0:27:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是習得依文的黑暗魔法的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.82,0:27:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己習得的  只屬於你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.69,0:27:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此驕傲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.39,0:27:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,習得師父的技能的證明…！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.74,0:27:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不要懈怠了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.81,0:27:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不過是剛剛得到了自己的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.12,0:27:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是今後
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.39,0:28:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.52,0:28:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那就馬上走吧  讓我看看你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.64,0:28:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.50,0:28:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…喂  說什麼馬上  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.46,0:28:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  千雨同學
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.66,0:28:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.41,0:28:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…十分感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.23,0:28:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…呃  都說不用道謝了…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.36,0:28:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個問題啦  老師不休息一下可不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.11,0:28:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的沒事的  他可睡了整整兩天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.58,0:28:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.79,0:28:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.01,0:28:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…絕對不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.13,0:28:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少先洗個澡吧  我說…喂！
